    // If l and r are very close, say l=19, r=29.
    // Multiples of 2: {20, 22, 24, 26, 28} -> 5 occurrences.
    // Multiples of 3: {21, 24, 27} -> 3 occurrences.
    // Multiples of 4: {20, 24, 28} -> 3 occurrences.
    // Multiples of 5: {20, 25} -> 2 occurrences.
    // ...
    // Multiples of 19: {19} -> 1 occurrence.
    //
    // In this case, 2 is the answer.
